f fear.  We look down on other species for the most part, and such an idea would reflect that.  How many iksars have gone beyond that precept of the religion and worked to improve faction with many races.  An iksar that would have remained KoS to all natural enemies would have held on to his beliefs and be rewarded based on there level of faction.  If your feared and hated through the entire planet, you have earned righteous rewards and CT's favor.  CT might send you on a quest that has you striking fear into the hearts of others.<br><br>Likewise, Paladins and Quellious monks would be given favor from showing compassion and tranquility, perhaphs some quests would have you performing acts to prove this.  <br><br>Either way, im looking for quests to yield rewards OTHER then equipment.  i want to see quests that yield a one shot non-MQ'able, consumable item that permanently raises a stat/resist/hitpoints/mana/natural skills such as h2h,2hb etc.  Kinda like AAXP results in a box.<br><br>3) I made this as a joke today in /gu, but it may actually turn out to be useful.  What if they added an equipment slot or 2.  (Do a quest, get your tounge/belly pierced for another earring <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>More please!<br>Azith<br> <p><a target="new" href = "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27884">Azith's Equipment</a><BR>There's no greater joy than helping people.<BR>Other than wiping out the entire raid "by accident".        - Fraxas </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uizzoe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Izzoe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 698<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(7/10/02 3:52:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromW